{"content":"<div class=\"fl_left jiathis_streak\"> \n <p class=\"title\"><label class=\"title\"><font color=\"#000000\">国家外专局行政许可事项公开目录</font></label></p> \n <p class=\"author\"><label class=\"author\">来自:外国专家局 时间:</label> 字体:<a href=\"#\" id=\"big_font\">大</a> <a href=\"#\" id=\"mid_font\">中</a> <a href=\"#\" id=\"sma_font\">小</a> </p> \n <p></p>\n <hr>\n <p></p> \n <p class=\"maincontent\">\n  <!--<label class=\"maincontent\">-->\n  <meta name=\"ContentStart\"></p>\n <div>\n  <div> \n   <p align=\"center\"> <strong>2015</strong><strong>年4月</strong></p> \n   <table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%\" width=\"100%\"> \n    <tbody> \n     <tr> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 49px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 项目<br> 编码</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 45px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 审批<br> 部门</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 101px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 项目名称</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 54px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 子项</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 43px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 审批</p> <p align=\"center\"> 类别</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 359px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 设定依据</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 59px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 共同审批部门</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 90px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 审批对象</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 114px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 收集意见联系电话及联系人</p> </td> \n     </tr> \n     <tr> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 49px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 50003</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 45px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 外专局</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 101px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 外国人来华工作许可</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 54px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 无</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 43px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 行政<br> 许可</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 359px\"> <p> 《国务院对确需保留的行政审批项目设定行政许可的决定》（国务院令第412号）第443项：外国人来华工作许可。</p> <p> 《中华人民共和国出境入境管理法》第四十一条规定：“外国人在中国境内工作，应当按照规定取得工作许可和工作类居留证件。任何单位和个人不得聘用未取得工作许可和工作类居留证件的外国人。”</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 59px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 无</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 90px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 国内聘请外国人单位</p> </td> \n      <td style=\"height: 1px; width: 114px\"> <p align=\"center\"> 68948899-50521</p> <p align=\"center\"> 魏玲</p> <p align=\"center\"> 68948899-50516</p> <p align=\"center\"> 耿鹏</p> </td> \n     </tr> \n    </tbody> \n   </table> \n   <div style=\"clear: both\"></div> \n  </div> \n  <p><br clear=\"all\"></p> \n </div>\n <!--</font>-->\n <meta name=\"ContentEnd\">\n <!--</label>-->\n <p></p> \n <br class=\"clear\"> \n <div style=\"width:703px;border-top:1px solid #c1c1c1;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div> \n <div style=\"float:left;\"> \n  <div class=\"jiathis_style\"> \n   <span class=\"jiathis_txt\">分享到：</span> \n   <a class=\"jiathis_button_qzone\">QQ空间</a> \n   <a class=\"jiathis_button_tsina\">新浪微博</a> \n   <a class=\"jiathis_button_tqq\">腾讯微博</a> \n   <a class=\"jiathis_button_renren\">人人网</a> \n   <a class=\"jiathis_button_kaixin001\">开心网</a> \n   <a href=\"http://www.jiathis.com/share\" class=\"jiathis jiathis_txt jiathis_separator jtico jtico_jiathis\" target=\"_blank\">更多</a> \n  </div> \n </div> \n <br class=\"clear\"> \n <br class=\"clear\"> \n <br class=\"clear\"> \n <!--百度推荐--> \n <!--<div><script>document.write(unescape('%3Cdiv id=\"hm_t_92668\"%3E%3C/div%3E%3Cscript charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"http://crs.baidu.com/t.js?siteId=1ccb3874f3daa5a2172ca81e7e5cd2ec&planId=92668&async=0&referer=') + encodeURIComponent(document.referrer) + '&title=' + encodeURIComponent(document.title) + '&rnd=' + (+new Date) + unescape('\"%3E%3C/script%3E'));</script></div>--> \n <!--百度推荐结束--> \n</div>","createTime":1518420140201,"modules":[],"pubTime":1518420140201,"sourceName":"中华人民共和国国家外国专家局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家外专局行政许可事项公开目录","url":"ht